      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STYLISH ROBBO (3) pinged the lids and led throughout to score last start (22.59) at this track in Mix 1/2/3 over 400m. The form out of her last race has been franked. The hardest to beat again. MY MACHINE (7) boasts a strong record this journey here with four wins and two minors from seven tries. Missed the frame latest (22.73) when seventh over 388m at Gosford in a NG. Looks well placed here and among the chances. SKINNY MARIE (2) went straight to the front and never headed when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when finished 5th and beaten 10 lengths at Grafton (25.83). Strong form has emerged from her last run. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. AUSSIE BELL (1) form at this distance reads well.",
